{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Yubin Song","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVrYPlmlkZSoFgSGiuvHvLFVUONf-QG94kW7_RBm8F0jt3ocIEbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are an adult patient who is considering to get a Invisalign for the teeth you've been thinking about for your entire life, I highly recommend 3rd and Columbia Dental. As an adult starting a ortho treatment for the first time, I was initially nervous about the process but Dr. Park was very attentive and took time to come up with the plan that will address my concerns so I decided to start the treatment. My two main concerns were crowded lower anterior teeth and narrow upper jaw. Before starting the treatment, Dr. Park clearly explained the treatment plan, timeline, expected results. Their dental assistances are also experienced and knowledgeable. My attachments barely came off during the whole process. Even as a first time ortho patient, I felt the treatment plan was well thought out, precisely moving my teeth without causing excessive pain. I'm currently done with my initial treatment and waiting for refinements sets but I'm already very happy with the results so far. My teeth are more straight and my facial asymmetry is improved. I'm breathing better because my upper jaw was expanded more. Do your research and get a consultation but I really think it's not too late to get your teeth fixed in your 30's.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2h15SYs9nqPt65HWfK5Xed4ejORfuSnlTzjQOxgwIEWtjv67zMRPP4pi7N0CiJ8z-JUHQEeDWoIXjBNhKBwhK8H2zSV3ETqsVzg3s4RgUt-zIVfG9N6Ngi7grFagNjSZTpqe8AqzZulSxE=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-12"},{"Name":"Jayanth Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfSXt5VLuD3Hpkpq5aU4qAZH7zq6WWA004ldAmauO27ian_Yf7yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellently run operation. From the Front-desk onwards, I had friendly smiling faces welcome me, and usher me in through the various steps that were required. The hygenist, Grace is exceptionally professional and patient. I haven't been to the dentist in a couple of years, post covid, and she took her time to do a tremendous job in cleaning my teeth.\n\nThe doctor was friendly, paid close attention to all my information that i had shared prior to visit, and was very friendly, attentive, and knowledgeable, in helping me understand my options. I got so lucky picking this spot. They're super good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabby S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhkBfpR0ZfISI3z4Jzds82v2ivTL-pYgkm83HbiTXv0F1X7rN1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really awesome practice. The hygienist are nice, gentle with the cleaning, and walk you through with what they are doing. Dr. Park is so kind and explains things in a digestible way. The office staff is friendly and helpful too. Would definitely recommend this practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Asia Larkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdWVkgPQtNGXPu2gfmCRosotxujnPjI3kXEVvTDPlBzMVCrZXNUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team here is great. They keep you informed along every step. They were super proactive in communication and very friendly in office. As a new patient getting set up can be overwhelming but they made the whole process smooth. I left feeling confident about the work they did and appreciate the care they provided.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve \u0026 Gwen Cover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjEY4wlniFF9Z4zCH6udnX4U1xR1bvlI5wT_uKPuw6PenvMV4H=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this office with an emergency while on travel. From my first call to Christine, I was seen within an hour. The appointment was on-time, smooth, and a great experience.  The doctor and team were very understanding of my situation and had me in and out so I could make a critical flight connection.  Thank you for being so kind.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Bennett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUINsl5ep8d032-fGRoqAx_FERHMF7p7tkdQXM8boaXOzNHiC4RIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Park and the team were great. Kind, thorough, and accommodating. They fixed my chipped front tooth after my exam even though I wasn’t scheduled for it, and it turned out beautiful!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Fischer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9SegaGemdtgVpya87mC85HTJyqFDbBJP1qJIY3SgWgr2Rrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to 3rd and Columbia dental more times in the last two years than I would like to count... my teeth :(  (cavities, cracked teeth, crown(s), cleaning) but every step of the way it has been an enjoyable experience!\nFrom walking into the office and immediately being greeted by the front desk staff, to a prompt check in and intake, taking your annual x-rays,  the procession of walking you to your chair (each space is pretty sectioned off so its like your own room). I've come to know a lot of the staff I normally see on a first name basis (heyyyy!), chairs are comfy, you get cute terminator glasses (see attached photo), a bib, and you're off to whatever you need to do.\nDr. David Park is just beyond, a professional and very sweet man.  Efficient, honest, and it's all just so easy. I have fallen asleep and laughed here more times than I would like to count with my mouth WIDE open.\nAnyways, just go, your teeth will thank you. Use your insurance, the dentist (especially when you look into the eyes of this one) isn't scary, and we all swoon for a beautiful smile.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3cdhA9e-4za1YQYEv3NfG2PlkLWPXjCtguXzHPuSWjflrbiTeZSkz4vv0G-YaaF49afiDnOXz5Az3GvmLnjVrEA2XDyoSiOAvt3moLTnsYa2XCP-D6-jLZ4e5Avgc9nXXRXu9JqqU1FjLj=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-30"},{"Name":"Joonhyuk Yun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYeXjXjKFz8HNOE5w33ba3PZn073n007vEcknp7BZ_GhyVAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The doctor and assistant were so kind and friendly! The doctor did a thorough dental exam but kept it quick and efficient.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
