me":"Diann Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlPNe3sEgLw67yfGKDExK4ANnO8f_RfKB_Kl9X1siHa5eCBHIR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding Care for Over a Decade\nI've been a patient at Seattle Dental Studio with Dr. Dbouk for over 10 years, and I can confidently say that the level of care here is exceptional. Dr. Dbouk combines remarkable technical skill with a calm, reassuring demeanor that instantly puts you at ease. Whether it's routine cleanings, crowns, implants, or more advanced cosmetic work, every treatment I've received has been done with precision and genuine care.\nWhat truly sets this practice apart is the consistently friendly, professional staff who make every visit smooth and pleasant. They're attentive, efficient, and always make you feel welcome.\nAfter a decade of excellent service, I wholeheartedly recommend Dr. Dbouk and Seattle Dental Studio to anyone seeking top-tier dental care in a warm and professional environment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patricia King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZ7oqRYBh2Vnu3z4R-CVj5a_Rai_NIL0LA4xrL5H1GPfPZ-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Dbouk and the team are all wonderful. I've been with this practice for many years. I have a real fear of dental procedures and have never experienced anything but kindness, compassion and respect...from scheduling to dental work to billing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brooke Hankins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLX928zVEOMDM5pn3D-WakOrvKMJfhHc9s68Ea-Me6i1ipR568=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great visit at this dental studio. I haven't been in a couple years and was a little nervous you never know the new dentist, but the staff here was super kind, professional, and knowledgeable.\n\nThey walked me through the whole process, and didn't pressure me into getting any sort of treatments or add-ons which I appreciated.\n\nI would highly recommend them to anyone in Seattle looking for a new dentist! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jaye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlldgXYDlXnlWtc16SLhgqmRioP-cajkacbu1II4HSCBV2GL4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My dental hygienist was an absolute delight.  I loved how she took pride in her work.  She said she was a perfectionist!!  Those are the best.  But also her willingness to share light personal stories and her love for crime shows 😳\n\nOf course Dr, Dbouk has a wonderfully refreshing and friendly, but professional chair side manner.  He seems to truly care about his patients and wants to provide the best possible dental guidance and care.,\n\nI admire him for leaving a flourishing practice to take his father on a once in a lifetime 2-week spiritual journey. That caring character spills over into his practice.\n\nMay his business, family, and staff be blessed.  Jaye","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Guido Tebano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEUS-qe4yr7MAjJLox1Nvy1G3kkGbZbG1nWG-0DuPnnrGB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Dbouk is absolutely amazing.  I work right by his office and was looking for a dentist that I could go by there. I am so happy I read his reviews and made an appointment.  I really am happy I told him I wanted a better smile. I am so happy with my new smile and it was totally resonable. Literally I cannot stop smiling.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liz Lord","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbp0q6CLzTCpdP2f6_gcasaXM8Q6SqcYajpp9wby2s9f3-HGcxqA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this office!\nDr. Dbouk is an expert at creating smiles. I’ve been in the dental field for 37 years, and I’m grateful to have met him - that he’s my doctor.  I travel across the country to see him because he’s worth it. If you want excellence, there is no other choice!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amber Dawn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwZE5e4ED7hW4eYIT50Qzv-UqxoFTmXBYiAhXekM8zqn00qw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Dr. Dbouk for almost 10 years. (My mouth was a nightmarescape when I first came in so I've experienced everything from cleaning to implants) His office has been so patient with me working through my financial limitations, payment plans, (covid too, they are and were so clean!) and also accommodating my inability to stay numb long through all of it, they're really the best you can hope for in a dentist. They also keep up with all the new technology so it's been pretty fascinating watching the new tools come in and I've got the teeth to show for it! They accept CareCredit also which is a bonus. Just make sure you're transparent and upfront about your payment needs etc so they can plan with you. Very kind, very gentle, and very understanding. I never want to go to another dentist for the rest of my life! (Please don't retire any time soon Dr. Dbouk !!!)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark McCarty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqfRCGt6D1ANZn3y_IJr00iZ4AXg4MIJ4pW728yzqvZGwQ0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As usual, the staff is professional and friendly. My dental assistant was top notch. All as good as expected!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
